krift.dk |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |editor-last=Balzer |editor-first=J\u00fcrgen |year=1966 |title=Carl Nielsen Centenary Essays |publisher=Dennis Dobson |ref=harv|asin=B0000CMZE0 }}\n* {{cite journal |last=Brincker |first=Benedikte |year=2008 |title=The role of classical music in the construction of nationalism: an analysis of Danish consensus nationalism and the reception of Carl Nielsen |journal=Nations and Nationalism|volume=14 |number=4 |pages=684\u2013699 |ref=harv |doi=10.1111/j.1469-8129.2008.00354.x}}\n* {{cite web |last=Burton |first=Anthony |date=4 November 2006 |title=Nielsen: Symphony No.5, Op.50 |work=CD Review: Building a Library Recommendations |publisher=BBC |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/radio3/cdreview/pip/12mwz/ |accessdate=23 July 2010 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |last=Cane |first=A. |date=Autumn 2014 |title=Thomas Jensen and the Nielsen tradition |journal=Classical Recordings Quarterly |issue=78 |pages=12\u201318 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web|title=Carl Nielsen Edition&nbsp;\u2013 Download |publisher=Royal Danish Library |url=http://www.kb.dk/en/nb/dcm/cnu/download.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012000331/http://www.kb.dk/en/nb/dcm/cnu/download.html |archivedate=12 October 2014 |url-status=dead }} Table of contents, including introductions and music scores.\n** {{cite book |title=Aladdin |editor1-last=Fanning |editor1-first=David |authorlink=David Fanning (musicologist) |year=2000 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=I. Stage Music |volume=8 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=[[ISMN]] M-66134-014-0 |isbn=978-87-598-1009-5 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_08_aladdin.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163308/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_08_aladdin.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Aladdin''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Cantatas 1 |editor1-last=Ahlgren Jensen |editor1-first=Lisbeth