r=2007 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=I. Incidental Music |volume=9 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-202-1 |isbn=978-87-598-5396-2 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_09_incidental_music_2.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163613/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_09_incidental_music_2.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Incidental Music 2''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Maskarade (Masquerade) |editor1-last=Fjelds\u00f8e |editor1-first=Michael |editor2-last=Foltmann |editor2-first=Niels Bo |editor3-last=Hauge |editor3-first=Peter |editor4-last=Bruunshuus Petersen |editor4-first=Elly |editor5-last=Flensborg Petersen |editor5-first=Kirsten |year=2001 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=I. Stage Music |volume=1 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-019-5 |isbn=978-87-598-1047-7 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_01_E_maskarade_1.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163339/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_01_E_maskarade_1.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Maskarade''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Orchestral Works 2 |editor1-last=Foltmann |editor1-first=Niels Bo |editor2-last=Hauge |editor2-first=Peter |year=2004 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=8 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-113-0 |isbn=978-87-598-1127-6 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_08_orchestral_works_2.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163328/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_08_orchestral_works_2.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Orchestral Works 2''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Piano and Organ Works |editor1-last=Fanning |editor1-first=David |editor2-last=Foltmann |editor2-first=Niels Bo |year=2006 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=12 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-201-4 |isbn=978-87-598-5395-5 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_12_piano_and_organ_works.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016172651/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_12_piano_and_organ_works.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Piano and Organ Works''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Saul and David |editor1-last=Foltmann |editor1-first=Niels Bo |editor2-last=Hauge |editor2-first=Peter |editor3-last=Krabbe |editor3-first=Niels |year=2002 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=I. Stage Music |volume=4 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-105-5 |isbn=978-87-598-1095-8 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_04_E_saul_og_david_1.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016165406/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_I_04_E_saul_og_david_1.pdf |url-status=live |archivedate=16 October 2014 |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Saul og David''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Songs |editor1-last=Foltmann |editor1-first=Niels Bo |editor2-last=Hauge |editor2-first=Peter |year=2009 |editor3-last=Bruunshuus Petersen |editor3-first=Elly |editor4-last=Flensborg Petersen |editor4-first=Kirsten |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=III. Vocal Music |volume=7 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-211-3 |isbn=978-87-598-1823-7 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_III_07_songs_4.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016174349/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_III_07_songs_4.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014  |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Songs''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Suite for String Orchestra |editor1-last=Hauge |editor1-first=Peter |year=2001 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=7 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-008-9 |isbn=978-87-598-1010-1 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_07_2_suite.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016174457/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_07_2_suite.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Suite for String Orchestra''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Symphony 3 Preface |editor-last=Foltmann |editor-first=Niels Bo<!--WorldCat, byline p. xx--> |year=1999<!--WorldCat--> |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=3 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library <!--|id=[[ISMN]] M-66134-??--> |isbn=978-87-598-0991-4 |url=http://img.kb.dk/ma/cn/forord/CNU_II_03_pr.pdf |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Symphony 3 Preface''}}}}\n* {{cite web |last=Caron |first=Jean-Luc |date=20 January 2013 |title=Les \u00e9l\u00e8ves de Carl Nielsen |trans-title=Carl Nielsen's students |language=fr |url=http://www.resmusica.com/2013/01/20/les-danois-xvi-les-eleves-de-carl-nielsen/ |work=ResMusica |accessdate=18 May 2015 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |last=Cenicola |first=Tony |date=21 December 2012 |title=A Hit Parade of Small Labels and Upstarts: The Best Classical Music Recordings of 2012 |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/21/arts/music/the-best-classical-music-recordings-of-2012.html|accessdate=3 May 2015 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Dolleris |first=Ludvig |year=1949 |title=Carl Nielsen |publisher=Fyns Boghandels |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |title=LSO celebrates Nielsen |publisher=Embassy of Denmark, United Kingdom |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725211338/http://www.amblondon.um.dk/en/menu/TheEmbassy/News/LSO%20celebrates%20