dense/personer/carl%20nielsens%20mors%20familie |archivedate=18 May 2015  }}\n* {{cite book |last=Lawson |first=Jack |date=22 May 1997 |title=Carl Nielsen |publisher=Phaidon |isbn=978-0-7148-3507-5 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia |last=Layton |first=Robert |title=Nielsen, Carl (August) |work=[[Oxford Companion to Music]] |edition=online |url=http://0-www.oxfordmusiconline.com.catalogue.ulrls.lon.ac.uk/subscriber/article/opr/t114/e4723|accessdate=6 May 2015 |ref=harv}}{{subscription}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Meyer |first1=Torben |last2=Petersen |first2=Frede Schandorf |year=1947 |title=Carl Nielsen Kunstneren og Mennesket Bind 1 |language=da |trans-title=Carl Nielsen the Artist and the Man Volume 1 |publisher=Nyt Nordisk Forlag. Arnold Busck |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |editor-last=Miller |editor-first=Mina F. |editor-link=Mina F. Miller |year=1994 |title=The Nielsen Companion |publisher=Faber and Faber |isbn=978-1-57467-004-2 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Nielsen |first=Carl |year=1953 |title=My Childhood |others=Translated from the Danish by Reginald Spink |url= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |title=Nielsen Notes |publisher=Carl Nielsen Society |url=http://carlnielsen.dk/pages/nielsen-notes.php |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211090846/http://carlnielsen.dk/pages/nielsen-notes.php |archivedate=11 February 2015<!-- not a dead url, but content looks likely to change with time--> |ref={{harvid|''Nielsen Notes''|2015}}}}\n* {{cite web |title=Welcome to Odense Symphony Orchestra |publisher=Odense Symphony Orchestra |url=http://odensesymfoni.dk/Webnodes/da/Web/Odense+Symfoniorkester/ENGLISH |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219110116/http://odensesymfoni.dk/Webnodes/da/Web/Odense%2BSymfoniorkester/ENGLISH |archivedate=19 February 2015 |url-status=dead |ref={{harvid|Odense Symphony Orchestra}} }}\n* {{cite book |last=Pankhurst |first=Tom |year=2008<!--page metadata on pdf file, 2010--> |chapter=Nielsen and 'Progressive tonality': a narrative approach