be |editor2-first=Niels |year=2002 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=III. Vocal Music |volume=1 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-102-4 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_III_01_cantatas_1.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163230/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_III_01_cantatas_1.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Cantatas 1''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Chamber Music 1 |editor1-last=Ahlgren Jensen |editor1-first=Lisbeth |editor2-last=Bruunshuus Petersen |editor2-first=Elly |editor3-last=Flensborg Petersen |editor3-first=Kirsten |year=2004 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=10 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-104-8 |isbn=978-87-598-1093-4 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_10_chamber_music_1.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016171023/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_10_chamber_music_1.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Chamber Music 1''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Helios |editor1-last=Hauge |editor1-first=Peter |editor2-last=Michelsen |editor2-first=Thomas |year=2001 |work=Carl Nielsen Works |series=II. Instrumental Music |volume=7 |publisher=The Carl Nielsen Edition, Royal Danish Library |id=ISMN M-66134-010-2 |isbn=978-87-598-1014-9 |url=http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_07_4_helios.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016163602/http://www.kb.dk/export/sites/kb_dk/da/nb/dcm/cnu/pdf/CNU_II_07_4_helios.pdf |archivedate=16 October 2014 |url-status=live |ref={{harvid|''Carl Nielsen Edition: Helios''}}}}\n** {{cite book |title=Incidental Music 2 |editor1-last=Bruunshuus Petersen |editor1-first=Elly |editor2-last=Flensborg Petersen |editor2-first=Kirsten |year=2007 |work=Carl N